reviewText: His Youtube lectures are better than this DVD
I especially got a lot out of the section on psychiatry.
inappropriately titled - disguising the author's rather extreme personal opinions.
I believe that freemason is not a conspiracy theory,chieft psychiatrist  and big farma are a member of freemason

I particularly wanted to see this video from the moment I saw it advertised. As someone who has been diagnosed as mentally ill I wanted to see the 'take' on it (I don't believe I'm mentally ill) I must say the video CONFIRMED all my suspicions and experiences (so its not just me)about psychiatrists and the mental health system. I recommend anyone who is in the same situation as me to watch this video. Very basically its the lunatics that are in charge of the asylum!!!
